== Reaction Formula ==
* With identifiers:
** 1 [[ATP]][c] '''+''' 1 [[AMINO-HYDROXYMETHYL-METHYL-PYR-P]][c] '''=>''' 1 [[AMINO-HYDROXYMETHYL-METHYLPYRIMIDINE-PP]][c] '''+''' 1 [[ADP]][c]
* With common name(s):
** 1 ATP[c] '''+''' 1 4-amino-2-methyl-5-(phosphooxymethyl)pyrimidine[c] '''=>''' 1 4-amino-2-methyl-5-(diphosphomethyl)pyrimidine[c] '''+''' 1 ADP[c]

